					<time datetime="2026-01-05T19:29:17-04:00">January 5, 2026 at 7:29 pm</time>				</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

							</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p><img class="wprm-comment-rating" src="https://chocolatewithgrace.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" /><br />
I am 71 and never ask for anything special but this year I asked for a blueberry cheesecake. My kids are in their 50&#8217;s and didn&#8217;t know this was my favorite.  Of course oven wasn&#8217;t available so she looked up recipes and found yours. This was so delicious.  Thank you and I won&#8217;t wait another 20 years to have this again.</p>
			</div><!-- .comment-content -->

			<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-81087" data-commentid="81087" data-postid="2599" data-belowelement="div-comment-81087" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Becky Cassels" aria-label="Reply to Becky Cassels">Reply</a></div>		</article><!-- .comment-body -->
