<p class="is-style-heading has-gigantic-font-size">Welcome</p>



<p>Hi! I’m Mary Younkin, and I'm thrilled that you are here. Chocolate with Grace features hundreds of recipes for tasty desserts and family-friendly meals. The recipes you’ll find here use everyday ingredients and simple techniques to create dishes with an abundance of flavor. But the heart behind what I do will always be to share good food with friends and family. </p>



